unittitle_ssm: Tamiment Library and Robert F. Wagner Labor Archives Collection of Law Serials
abstract_ssm: The Tamiment Library and Robert F. Wagner Labor Archives Collection of Law Serials contains over 180 titles on legal issues in the United States, Europe, and Central America between 1935 and 2013.  The bulk of the collection consists of American serials published between the 1960s and the 1980s.  Topics include the legal system in the United States, human rights issues, and prison reform.
